snippet.title: Matter : PC Trailer | Concrete Games
snippet.description:
Explore a mystic and expressive world in a dynamic first person plateformer. Dive in a dreamlike and abstract world where matter evolves and lives around you according to your actions.

Release date: Tuesday, December 18, 2018

Presskit : https://www.concretegames.xyz/matter-presskit/

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/978250/Matter/
Itch.io: https://concretegames.itch.io/matter
Website: https://www.concretegames.xyz/matter-info
